<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99600171224153></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99600171224153><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/news/sdetail.html?story=159&mid=99600171224153 style='color: darkblue;'>good review, but missing stuff</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/poster.html?id=39872><span id=Scholar>lorddaeth</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>50 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Jul 24th 3:08 PM</td>
