<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99599956023910></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99599956023910><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/news/sdetail.html?story=159&mid=99599956023910 style='color: darkblue;'>Has the Writer even Played AO?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></td></tr>
